Exception Handling :
    -The process of catching the exception for converting JVM exception message to end user readable message.
    -Catching this abnormal termination of the programm is know as Exception Handling.
    -To stop the abnormal termination
    -There are two types of exception handling
        1. Compile time error : Error before the compilation.
        2. Run time error : These error are know as exceptions. Catching this abnormal termination of the programm is know as Exception Handling

    